headline: Corpay Cross-Border Extends Exclusive Partnership with West Ham United
summary: TORONTO, June 17, 2025--Corpay, Inc.*, (NYSE: CPAY) a global leader in corporate payments, is pleased to announce that Corpay’s Cross-Border business has entered into a multi-year agreement to extend their successful and exclusive collaboration with West Ham United as their Official Foreign Exchange (FX) and International Payments Partner.
